      home_hero_title: 'Turn Any Photo Into a<br><em>Diamond Painting</em> Pattern',
      home_hero_desc: 'Upload your photo, choose your canvas size, and instantly generate a full DMC color-coded diamond painting pattern — complete with bead counts and printable symbols.',
