      home_feat_subtitle: 'Diamond Painter converts your image using professional-grade color quantization algorithms, the same technology used by commercial diamond painting suppliers.',
      home_feat1_title: 'AI Color Quantization', home_feat1_desc: 'Our intelligent algorithm reduces your image to 5–80 perfectly matched DMC colors, preserving the essence of your photo while keeping the bead count manageable.',
