      home_why_label: 'Why Diamond Painter', home_why_title: 'The pattern tool that actual crafters use',
      home_why_subtitle: 'Built by someone who knows what it is like to squint at a tiny pattern or waste an order because the color count was off.',
      home_ben1_title: 'Instant Preview', home_ben1_desc: 'See your pattern update live as you adjust settings — no waiting for renders.',
      home_ben2_title: 'Accurate Colors', home_ben2_desc: 'DMC codes are matched using perceptual color distance, not just RGB proximity.',
